-MmayAMnUY7w8ghp4qVD.text: An additional report states that a detached garage is on fire. There might possibly be a welding tank inside the garage reportedly. Firefighters are en route.

-Mmayj7W6o0XFnAk44Mq.text: Firefighters are at the scene and have reported smoke and fire seen in the single-story garage.

-Mmaz4WTvfJ1NVI_XefJ.text: Firefighters are getting water on the fire at the back door of the garage.

-Mmb-lW7NIg8T9dXYar9.text: No one is trapped in the fire reportedly.

-Mmb-xd_FdZzv0xV_9V4.text: Firefighters have reported that the fire is under control. They will be investigating further.

-Mmb27ABy-slWlZme7sw.text: Firefighters have requested Police at the scene for further investigation.
